## Adding New Translations

### 1. Edit ARB Files

Location: `lib/l10n/`

**intl_en.arb:**
```json
{
  "@newKey": {
    "description": "Description of the string"
  },
  "newKey": "English text"
}
```

**intl_ar.arb:**
```json
{
  "@newKey": {
    "description": "Description of the string"
  },
  "newKey": "النص العربي"
}
```

### 2. Generate

```bash
flutter gen-l10n
```

### 3. Use in Code

```dart
Text(AppLocalizations.of(context)!.newKey)
```

