## Date/Number Formatting

Use `intl` package for locale-aware formatting:

```dart
import 'package:intl/intl.dart' as intl;

// Get locale
final locale = ref.watch(localeProvider);

// Date formatting
final dateFormat = intl.DateFormat.yMMMMd(locale.languageCode);
final formattedDate = dateFormat.format(DateTime.now());
// ar: ٣٠ نوفمبر ٢٠٢٥
// en: November 30, 2025

// Number formatting
final numberFormat = intl.NumberFormat.decimalPattern(locale.languageCode);
final formattedNumber = numberFormat.format(1234.56);
// ar: ١٬٢٣٤٫٥٦
// en: 1,234.56

// Currency formatting
final currencyFormat = intl.NumberFormat.currency(
  locale: locale.languageCode,
  symbol: 'SAR',
);
```

